Prerequisites:
    All previous installations and setup will be needed for the API to work as is
    Make sure that the API project works (recommended to download the EF-API project from GitHub for proper setup):
    cd api
    dotnet watch run
 
Installations:
    **Install 8.0.0 versions
    Microsoft.Extensions.Identity.Core
    Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity.EntityFrameworkCore
    Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer

Comments from author:
* Comments // have been removed from previous API project.
* You will have to migrate the API to your Microsoft DB. Previous project contains instructions on how to do that. //Might add later